videos.description: Luke Skipper throws a 41-yard strike to Nigel Carter for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Tulsa offense strikes first

videos.description: SMU's Ben Hicks finds Trey Quin for a 7-yard touchdown to tie the game at 7-7.
videos.headline: Hicks, Quin tie game with TD

videos.description: Luke Skipper completes a 49-yard pass to Justin Hobbs putting the Golden Hurricanes in great field position.
videos.headline: Tulsa making splash plays early

videos.description: Tulsa RB Shamari Brooks shakes the defender and scores the touchdown to give the Golden Hurricane a 14-7 lead.
videos.headline: Brooks sweet move puts Tulsa ahead

videos.description: QB Chad President fakes the hand-off and keeps it himself to score an 8-yard touchdown, putting  SMU up 21-7.
videos.headline: President extends SMU's lead

videos.description: D'Angelo Brewer is trapped in the backfield but makes a nifty move to score the touchdown.
videos.headline: Brewer makes great cut for TD

videos.description: Ben Hicks completes a 23-yard touchdown to Trey Quinn for his second score of the day.
videos.headline: Mustangs' Quinn scores second TD of the game

videos.description: Luke Skipper throws a deep ball to Justin Hobbs who makes a terrific one-handed grab for a touchdown, but the score is wiped away because of a unsportsmanlike conduct penalty for  his celebration going into the end zone.
videos.headline: Hobbs makes great catch, penalty takes away TD

videos.description: RB Ke'mon Freeman takes the reverse hand-off then throws it to Trey Quinn for a 28-yard reception.
videos.headline: SMU digs into their bag of tricks for long gain

videos.description: Ke'Mon Freeman runs it in for a 2-yard touchdown to pull SMU within 3 points in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Freeman's TD narrows the gap

videos.description: Ben Hicks finds Courtland Sutton for a 42-yard catch, putting them at midfield.
videos.headline: SMU offense connects on a huge play

videos.description: RB Xavier Jones bounces it to the left and speeds into the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Jones' TD gives Mustangs the lead

videos.description: The Mustangs use a flea flicker and Ben Hicks fires a pass down field to Courtland Sutton for a 44-yard gain.
videos.headline: SMU offense uses razzle dazzle for long gain

videos.description: Tulsa's Luke Skipper scrambles to his right and throws to the end zone, but Rodney Clemons is there for the interception.
videos.headline: Skipper throws costly interception
